is hiring 2-3 Junior/Senior Corporate Lawyers
Tavernier Tschanz is a leading Swiss corporate boutique law firm that enjoys a reputation of excellence in the market and among its clients in the fields of corporate transactions, corporate/commercial law, tax, as well as international commercial arbitration and litigation.

We assist a very diverse clientele of large global companies, PE and VC funds, institutional investors, as well as successful SME companies, technology start-ups and entrepreneurs. Our clients span a large range of industries, such as energy, utilities, education, manufacturing, IT and new technologies, life sciences and pharma, media, automotive and transport, luxury, hotels, banking and finance, international trade, real estate, distribution and retail, as well as marketing and sports.

Our corporate lawyers have strong expertise in corporate finance, advising on all types of transactions, such as M&A, takeovers, LBOs, MBOs, MBIs, restructuring, divestitures, spin-offs, PE and VC financings, as well as general domestic and international finance.

